user.biography:
Official Page of Montauk Brewing Company + Montauk Hard Seltzer - Must be 21+ to follow.
“Come As You Are”

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company with @jjamet, @creich910, @breich84, and @montaukcyclecompany. May be an image of one or more people, people riding bicycles, people standing, bicycle and road.

node.text: A couple of years ago we started this thing called Hot Laps where a few friends would meet up at the brewery every Thursday around 5:15PM, race a few miles around a loop in Montauk as fast as possible and then finish with a celebratory pint @montaukbrewco - It’s unsanctioned and quite dangerous, it’s like Fight Club but instead of not talking about it, we talk about it with anyone who will listen. Maybe we should look into making this a sanctioned thing, just maybe. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be a closeup of fruit.

node.text: Fresh blueberries grown right here in Montauk will be the perfect addition to a light and crisp beer that will be available soon on tap exclusively @montaukbrewco - Stay tuned for new and exciting innovations coming out of the Brew Barn in the next few weeks! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Montauk Brewing Co. on August 09, 2021 tagging @dexterlakeclubband, and @whalebonemagazine. May be an image of one or more people, drink and outdoors.

node.text: A little birthday shindig for our friends @whalebonemagazine happened on a Friday a couple of weeks ago here in Montauk. We brought a few hundred, maybe a few thousand cans of beer to the party. Seems like people really enjoyed them. Here’s to more parties, more music, and much more beer! #montauk #comeasyouare 📸 @jamesmorano

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of dog and body of water.

node.text: If Sunday was a vibe, this might be it right here. Hope everyone had a great weekend filled with cold @montaukbrewco beers! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of drink and outdoors.

node.text: Here we have two summertime favorites. On the left is our Jalapeño Watermelon Session and on the right we have the new Mango Haze IPA! Have you tried these limited releases yet!? Enjoy them on tap exclusively @montaukbrewco #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. on August 06, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, dog and outdoors.

node.text: Happy Friday to all of our incredible @montaukbrewco fans! August is upon us and prime summer weather is here, so be sure to stock up on Montauk Summer Ale and Watermelon Session six packs while you still can! Stay tuned for upcoming beer releases and new comfy wearables coming soon. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of drink and outdoors.

node.text: Cheers to another National Day we can get behind. Happy National IPA Day to all you IPA lovers! Grab a six pack and head over to the link in our bio for assorted @montaukbrewco IPA glassware. #montauk #comeasyouare #nationalipaday

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Empire State Building with @whalebonemagazine. May be an image of fruit, cosmetics and text.

node.text: Thank you to the pioneering individual who first created National Watermelon Day. Turns out that day is today and the weather is perfect for an ice cold Watermelon Session Ale. Grab a six pack and enjoy on the beach, stoop, rooftop, backyard, boat…you get the idea! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk, New York. May be an image of drink and text that says 'COME AS YOU ARE"N BREWING WEN YORK-ESTABLISHED MONTAUK SUMMER ALE" CRAFT BEER 12 FL oz'.

node.text: The answer is yes, Montauk Pumpkin Ale will be coming back soon-ish. For now, hold on to Summer Vibes with ice cold Montauk Summer Ale. Stock up while you can! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Inlet Seafood Restaurant. May be an image of twilight, nature, sky and ocean.

node.text: Saturday Vibes are quite strong right now, we can feel it. Hope everyone had a great day and is gearing up for an awesome night! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Last year we brewed a beer that we named Green Toucan. Our fans request this beer in the taproom quite often so it seemed fitting to bring the bird back before summer ends. Plan on being in Montauk on 9/2 for a 4-pack of Green Toucan IPA and a hefty helping of good vibes as per usual. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of drink.

node.text: On August 19th we will be releasing a very special Ocean Series beer called Beach Break Double IPA. Beach Break clocks in at 7.5% ABV and is brewed with Idaho 7 and Mosaic hops. Think tropical, pineapple, and citrus aromas galore - that’s Beach Break! #montauk #comeasyouare
